name: Love waifu #203 - Forest Encounters
description: Dappled sunlight filters through the trees, casting shadows over her glossy latex-clad body. Sitting with her legs slightly parted, she toys with a strand of hair, lost in thought — or is she imagining your hands tracing the seams of her outfit? Her green eyes flick up, catching your gaze. The forest isn’t the only thing that’s wild.

attributes.value: The "Love Waifu" collection is a series of unique digital artworks featuring anime-style female characters in diverse emotional states and situations. Each NFT heroine isn't just a character — she's a moment suspended between temptation, vulnerability, and playful power. Enter a world where a single look can say more than any line of dialogue.
